{"product_id":"vengeance-wolf","title":"VENGEANCE WOLF","description":"\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM.\r\n100% French Terry Cotton.\r\nBeads work at the armhole area.\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nBoxy-Fit.\r\nCombed\r\nBio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCrafted from heavyweight 240 GSM cotton, this oversized sleeveless vest brings raw street attitude with uncompromising quality. The front features a fierce wild wolf snarling under the bold gothic VENGEANCE typography — a symbol of power, rebellion, and untamed spirit. Detailed with beadwork along the armholes, this piece delivers a rugged edge that elevates the silhouette. Iconic biohazard and medic insignias sit beneath the artwork, cementing its post-apocalyptic streetwear vibe.\r\n\r\nThe back carries the VENGEANCE wordmark again with the signature DRIP STUDIOS insignia, marking it as a drop forged in fury.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the vest inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the vest in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eVest with 240 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46853860622490,"sku":"vest(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46853860655258,"sku":"vest(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853860688026,"sku":"vest(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"